description: This file is a test script written using the Playwright testing framework for end-to-end testing of a web application. It tests the performance of adding 100 nodes without UI lag regression by automating browser interactions and measuring elapsed time.

methods.name: test
methods.description: Defines a test case for adding 100 nodes in the web application and measuring performance.

methods.name: expect
methods.description: Assertions to verify that the web application's UI behaves as expected, including timing constraints and element visibility.
